frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature construction workers seemingly preparing a large dish of rice and chicken. The tiny figures, wearing yellow hard hats, are positioned around the food, creating an imaginative culinary construction site. In the background, a chef appears to be observing the scene while enjoying a meal.
